# 🎨 Salati — Visily Prompts (الشاشات الناقصة)

---

## Prompt 7: Settings — Appearance Tab (المظهر)

```
Design an Appearance settings panel for "Salati" Islamic prayer reminder desktop app.

This is the "Appearance" tab content inside a dark settings slide panel (right side, 350px wide).
Colors: Panel bg #161B22, cards #1C2128, green #1B8A6B, gold #C8A96E, text #E6EDF3, muted #8B949E.

Left edge: 4 vertical icon tabs (same as other settings screens):
- 🕐 المواعيد (Prayer Times)
- 🔔 التنبيهات (Alerts)
- 🎨 المظهر (Appearance) — ACTIVE with green indicator line
- ⚙️ عام (General)

PANEL TITLE: "🎨 المظهر | Appearance"
Close ✕ button top-right.

SECTION 1 — "الثيم | Theme":
Two theme cards side by side (each ~140x120px):

Card 1 — SELECTED (green border glow, green checkmark ✓ at top-right):
- Small dark preview rectangle showing mini mockup (dark bg, tiny green elements)
- Icon: 🌙
- Title: "Midnight Serenity"
- Subtitle: "داكن | Dark" — muted text
- Green border (#1B8A6B), subtle glow

Card 2 — NOT SELECTED (dim border, no checkmark):
- Small light preview rectangle (beige bg, tiny dark elements)
- Icon: ☀️
- Title: "Golden Dawn"
- Subtitle: "فاتح | Light" — muted text
- Gray border, subtle

SECTION 2 — "اللغة | Language":
Two language cards side by side (each ~140x80px):

Card 1 — SELECTED (green border):
- "العربية" — large text
- "Arabic" — small muted below
- Green checkmark ✓

Card 2 — NOT SELECTED:
- "English" — large text
- "الإنجليزية" — small muted below
- Gray border

Bottom: Green gradient "💾 حفظ | Save" button.

Note: Selection is click-to-toggle. Only one theme and one language can be active.
Clean, minimal, consistent with other tabs.
```

---

## Prompt 8: Settings — General Tab (عام)

```
Design a General settings panel for "Salati" Islamic prayer reminder desktop app.

This is the "General" tab content inside a dark settings slide panel (right side, 350px wide).
Colors: Panel bg #161B22, cards #1C2128, green #1B8A6B, gold #C8A96E, text #E6EDF3, muted #8B949E.

Left edge: 4 vertical icon tabs:
- 🕐 المواعيد
- 🔔 التنبيهات
- 🎨 المظهر
- ⚙️ عام (General) — ACTIVE with green indicator line

PANEL TITLE: "⚙️ عام | General"
Close ✕ button top-right.

SECTION 1 — "بدء التشغيل | Startup" card (dark bg #1C2128, rounded 12px):
4 toggle rows, each row has: [Label text] ... [Toggle switch on right]

Row 1: "تشغيل مع بداية الويندوز | Start with Windows"    [✅ ON — green]
Row 2: "تصغير عند البدء | Minimize on start"              [⬜ OFF — gray]
Row 3: "إظهار في System Tray"                              [✅ ON — green]
Row 4: "تصغير لـ Tray عند الإغلاق | Close to tray"        [✅ ON — green]

Toggle switches: rounded pill style, green (#1B8A6B) when ON, gray (#484F58) when OFF.
Subtle separator lines between rows.

SECTION 2 — "البيانات | Data" card:
Two buttons stacked:
- "🔄 إعادة ضبط الإعدادات | Reset to Defaults" — outline button (green border, no fill, text green)
- "📂 فتح مجلد الإعدادات | Open Settings Folder" — outline button (gray border, text muted)

SECTION 3 — "عن التطبيق | About" (no card, just text):
- 🕌 "Salati v1.0.0" — white text, medium
- "صنع بـ ❤️ بواسطة فريق Salati" — muted, small
- "Made with ❤️ by Salati Team"
- Link style text: "🔗 GitHub" — green underline text

Bottom: Green gradient "💾 حفظ | Save" button.

Clean, organized, consistent toggle style with the Alerts tab.
```

